panels.name: Threat Resolve Marking
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "Threat marked as resolved"
| parse "filePath=*" as path
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|*|rt=" as os,startcode,message,endcode
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, message, path

panels.name: Updates and Installs Areas
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" (*update* or *install*)
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|1|suser=* ip=* rt=" as it_code,startcode,message,machine,remote_ip
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = remote_ip
| if (isNull(country_code), "unknown", country_code) as country_code
| if (isNull(region), "unknown", region) as region
| if (isNull(city), "unknown", city) as city
| if (isNull(postal_code), "unknown", postal_code) as postal_code
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code
| sort _count

panels.name: Commissioning
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" *commission*
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|Machine * *|*|rt=" as os,startcode,machine,action,endcode
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, machine, os, action
| sort by machine asc
| fields - _count

panels.name: Updates by Machine and IP
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" (*update* or *install*)
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|1|suser=* ip=* rt=" as it_code,startcode,message,machine,remote_ip
| fields - it_code, startcode, message
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, machine, remote_ip
| fields - _count
| sort by machine asc

panels.name: Event Breakdown
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" SentinelOne
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|*|" as os_code,startcode,message,endcode
| if(message matches "Quarantine*", "quarantine actions", message) as message
| if(message matches "Kill*", "kill actions", message) as message
| if(message matches "*threat*" or message matches "Threat*", "threat actions", message) as message
| if(message matches "*update*", "machine updates", message) as message
| if(message matches "*subscribed*", "machine subscriptions", message) as message
| if(message matches "*commission*", "machine commissions", message) as message
| if(message not in("quarantine actions","kill actions","threat actions","machine updates","machine subscriptions","machine commissions"), "other", message) as message
| count message

panels.name: Threat Quarantines
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" quarantine
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|*|suser=* " as os,startcode,message,endcode,machine
| parse field=message "* performed successfully" as action
| timeslice 1d
| count _timeslice, action, machine
| sort by machine asc

panels.name: Quarantine Areas
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" quarantine
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|Quarantine performed successfully|*|suser=* ip=* rt=" as os,startcode,endcode,machine,remote_ip
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = remote_ip
| if (isNull(country_code), "unknown", country_code) as country_code
| if (isNull(region), "unknown", region) as region
| if (isNull(city), "unknown", city) as city
| if (isNull(postal_code), "unknown", postal_code) as postal_code
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code
| sort _count

panels.name: Threat Kills
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" kill
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|*|*|suser=* " as os,startcode,message,endcode,machine
| parse field=message "* performed successfully" as action
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, action, machine
| sort by machine asc

panels.name: Threat by Machine
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "New active threat"
| parse "<14>CEF:0|SentinelOne|Mgmt|*|*|* - machine *|*|rt=" as os,startcode,message,machine,endcode nodrop
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, message, machine
| sort by machine asc
